OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FScottish Green co-leader Ross Greer
OL,8,Fhas said he is "not interested" in
OL,9,Fbecoming First Minister.
OL,11,FMr Greer co-leads the Scottish Green
OL,12,FParty with Gillian Mackay ` whom he
OL,13,Fsaid he would happily serve as deputy
OL,14,Ffirst minister.
OL,16,FThe most recent YouGov poll predicted
OL,17,Fthe Scottish greens could win 11 seats
OL,18,Fin the election, meaning they would
OL,19,Fneed to gain a significant amount of
OL,20,Fsupport to beat the SNP's predicted 67
OL,21,Fseats.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@_O]
