PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Press Association, Mr
OL,8,FGreer said: "I am quite genuinely not
OL,9,Finterested in becoming the first
OL,10,Fminister of Scotland, and I would be
OL,11,Funbelievably proud to serve as the
OL,12,Fdeputy to first minister Gillian
OL,13,FMackay.
OL,15,F"I have a style of politics that I
OL,16,Fthink leans towards just getting stuck
OL,17,Finto the details and back rooms and
OL,18,Fmake sure that policies get delivered."
OL,20,FMr Greer was the youngest MSP elected
OL,21,Fin the 2016 election at 21 years old.
OL,26,@pD@MOUwD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
