PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FHe has been a member of the Scottish
OL,8,FGreens since he was 15 and was a
OL,9,Fmember of the Scottish Youth
OL,10,FParliament, representing the Clydebank
OL,11,Fand Milngavie constituency between
OL,12,F2011 and 2013.
OL,14,FHe rose to be leader of the party in
OL,15,F2025 alongside Ms Mackay.
OL,17,FMs Mackay is the only female party
OL,18,Fleader on the campaign trail and has
OL,19,Fserved as co-leader of the party since
OL,20,Flast August, having given birth to her
OL,21,Ffirst child in June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
