PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FHer work in Parliament has often
OL,8,Ffocused on social justice and health,
OL,9,Fwhich Mr Greer said would be the
OL,10,Freason Ms Mackay would be the "kind of
OL,11,Fpolitician" the people of Scotland
OL,12,Fwould want.
OL,14,FMr Greer continued: "I think Gillian
OL,15,FMackay is the kind of politician that
OL,16,Fthe people of Scotland want to see.
OL,26,@rD@_OUsD@KO]vD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
