OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"Gillian has the depth of knowledge
OL,8,Fabout areas of public policy that
OL,9,Fpeople really care about, like our
OL,10,FNHS, and the kind of compassion that
OL,11,Fwe should want to see in our political
OL,12,Fleaders.
OL,14,F"So, as much as we co lead the party
OL,15,Fon an equal basis, in the event that
OL,16,Fwe are facing a Green majority
OL,17,Fgovernment on the seventh of May, I
OL,18,Fwill probably be calling her from my
OL,19,Fcount to her count to congratulate
OL,20,FScotland's first Green first minister,
OL,21,FGillian Mackay."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
