PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FMr Greer told the Press Association he
OL,8,Fhad not told Ms Mackay of his plans,
OL,9,Fhe said: "I've not told her yet that
OL,10,Fyet, though, breaking the news to
OL,11,FGillian that she will be the next
OL,12,Ffirst minister through PA Media."
OL,14,FThe party announced its manifesto on
OL,15,FTuesday with pledges to improve
OL,16,Fchildcare, offer free bus travel to
OL,17,Fall and a hard stance on no new North
OL,18,FSea oil and gas drilling.
OL,26,@qD@JOUtD@aO]
