OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FThe Scottish Greens have previously
OL,8,Fworked alongside the SNP in government
OL,9,Fto successfully achieve a number of
OL,10,Fpolicies including ending peak rail
OL,11,Ftickets.
OL,13,FWhile the latest YouGov poll shows the
OL,14,FSNP is predicted to win 67 seats and
OL,15,Fan outright majority, if they fell
OL,16,Fshort of that, that could open the way
OL,17,Ffor another deal with the Scottish
OL,18,FGreens, who are predicted to pick up
OL,19,F11 seats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
