PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FHowever, Mr Greer said that the
OL,8,FScottish Greens would only join a
OL,9,Fgovernment "serious about tackling the
OL,10,Fclimate emergency".
OL,12,FHe said: "Clearly, if we're in the
OL,13,Fevent of government formation and the
OL,14,FGreens are invited into that, we would
OL,15,Fonly join a government that was
OL,16,Fserious about tackling the climate
OL,17,Femergency.
OL,26,@qD@LOUrD@RO]tD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
