PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"Licensing decisions in the North Sea
OL,8,Fare reserved to the UK government, but
OL,9,Fthere are huge areas where the
OL,10,FScottish government could be taking
OL,11,Fmore action to tackle the climate
OL,12,Fcrisis.
OL,14,F"What the Greens want to see is a real
OL,15,Ffocus on investment in the sectors
OL,16,Fthat will create high-quality jobs in
OL,17,Fgreen industries, whatever decisions
OL,18,Fgovernments of any stripe make in
OL,19,FEdinburgh or in London, North Sea oil
OL,20,Fand gas is in decline.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
