PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776301390
OL,3,CScottish Greens co-leader Ross Greer:
OL,4,CI'm not interested in being First
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"People are losing their jobs already.
OL,8,FWe need to replace those jobs. We need
OL,9,Fto give people new jobs to move into
OL,10,Fso the Greens would want to be part of
OL,11,Fthe government double down on
OL,12,Finvestment in renewables, in the clean
OL,13,Fheat sector."
